data.description: Welcome Home! This beautiful townhome community is ready made for stress free living on the coast! This 3 bed 2.5 bath unit boasts an open floorplan on the main level with low maintenance wood flooring and stainless steel appliances. The upstairs bedrooms offer generous closets, as well as a private ensuite in the master. HOA maintains the yard, so no yardwork or exterior maintenance. Backyard has vinyl fencing and owners have added a storm door. Just move in and enjoy the life! You are only a few miles from the beach and all of the extras our vibrant little beach community has to offer. More photos coming next month. Currently occupied, but available for showings. Please contact agent for details.
